# Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

X-Mas Tic-Tac-Toe


## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

A two-player tic-tac-toe game that is Christmas themed.


## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

My software will be able to have two players play against each other in tic-tac-toe. Each player will be able to choose which space to move to, and it will keep track and decide who wins. I will execute this through IDLE.


